{"word":"ἐπίκλοπος","slug":"ἐπίκλοπος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπίκλοπος</b></el> <el>(ἐπί-κλοπος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κλέπτω'><el>κλέπτω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>thievish, wily</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>ἐπίκλοπος μύθων</el> <i>cunning in</i> speech, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}